modules.description: Provides functions to retrieve current process memory usage metrics, including resident set size and virtual memory size. Works with platform-specific data structures to expose system-level memory statistics. Used to monitor application resource consumption during performance analysis or debugging.

Provides functions to retrieve system memory usage information and format byte values with customizable output. Works with integer byte counts and a structured record type containing memory statistics. Used to display human-readable memory sizes in applications requiring precise control over unit formatting and presentation.
